      <title>人工智能估值担忧再起，芯片制造商拖累亚洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/sk-hynix-slides-weighing-on-korean-stocks-after-rout-in-nvidia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人工智能股市过热的担忧再度升温的背景下，亚洲半导体相关股票暴跌，区域基准指数有望创下一个月以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/sk-hynix-slides-weighing-on-korean-stocks-after-rout-in-nvidia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
